<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="maybe-adv">maybe <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'meɪbi/    美 /'meɪbi/  </p>
<p>[句子副词]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-perhaps">1.★ <strong>或许；大概 (perhaps)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Maybe she is working at the lab. 
她也许正在实验室工作。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Do you think he will come on time? 
你认为他会准时到吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Maybe. / <strong>Maybe not</strong>.
也许会吧。/可能不会。</p></div></div>